from everyone.

515
00:48:00,224 --> 00:48:03,716
I want to hear your love.

516
00:48:22,146 --> 00:48:27,743
Throughout the maze of this city,
The fallen people wander 'round,

517
00:48:28,018 --> 00:48:31,681
Pound the walls
and sigh, saying,

518
00:48:33,190 --> 00:48:38,685
I will return to that day,

519
00:48:39,029 --> 00:48:42,863
This is just like
a world of games for you.

520
00:48:44,868 --> 00:48:48,531
My eyes overflow
with tears now,

521
00:48:50,374 --> 00:48:53,707
But I don't want
to cry anymore.

522
00:48:55,546 --> 00:48:58,640
In every heart now,
you are, Angel.

523
00:48:58,749 --> 00:49:00,774
And you know it, Angel.

524
00:49:00,884 --> 00:49:05,412
You can never doubt
the trueness of you.

525
00:49:06,257 --> 00:49:09,556
The lie you thought you forgot
is alive,

526
00:49:09,660 --> 00:49:12,220
Coloring all the winds.

527
00:49:12,329 --> 00:49:16,993
And so, go and throw
all of your light,

528
